{"expireTime":9007200831408041000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-a325fd95243179f0429f377c84fd2515-gatsby-remark-relative-imagesgatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-copy-linked-files-","val":"<p>  Let's go through this topic and play with this fun toy !</p>\n<h2>A little history</h2>\n<p>I first tested the Kano OS to play with the story mode, here is a video I found to get a taste of it : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EE3F9xBoHoQ\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EE3F9xBoHoQ</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bd38243240e9307e8baec5aa3f224405/e7068/kano-color.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kano os\"\n        title=\"kano os\"\n        src=\"/static/bd38243240e9307e8baec5aa3f224405/e7068/kano-color.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd38243240e9307e8baec5aa3f224405/ba1ca/kano-color.jpg 512w,\n/static/bd38243240e9307e8baec5aa3f224405/e937d/kano-color.jpg 1024w,\n/static/bd38243240e9307e8baec5aa3f224405/e7068/kano-color.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>It is a super original way to explain how a computer works. Using an old-RPG look'n feel, and a little gameplay to discover the map (based on computer's parts). It is good to refresh memory for the one knowing already the basics, and the new comers will enjoy a more user friendly way to learn computer science.</p>"}